<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>About Us - PS Curves</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lavishly+Yours&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300..700&display=swap');
    
    .about-container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 40px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
    }

    .about-text {
      flex: 1;
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .about-text h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .about-text p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-image-wrapper {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-image {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-container {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .about-text h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/_navbar') %>


  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-text">
      <h1>About PS Curves</h1>
      <p><strong>PS Curves</strong> was born out of a passion for redefining style and self-expression through carefully curated fashion pieces. We believe in more than just trends — we believe in the power of individuality.</p>
      <p>What started as a small project quickly grew into a brand that celebrates creativity, quality, and uniqueness. Every product you find on our store is hand-picked and designed with purpose, ensuring that our customers feel empowered in what they wear.</p>
      <p>Our journey has only just begun — and we’re thrilled to have you along for the ride.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-image-wrapper">
      <img src="/Images/About Us.png" alt="About PS Curves" class="about-image" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/_footer') %>
</body>
</html>
